Actions 

a)  Further analysis of the gender split into the application for and award of bonus 

payments relating to consultant medical staff 
 

b)  Gender  analysis  undertaken  in  relation  to  the  Trusts  leadership  talent 

management work 
 

c)  Further analysis of the mean and median average pay gaps with the omission 
of  medical  staff  from  the  results  as  there  are  indications  that  it  is  this  staff 
group which has the most significant impact on the gender pay gap. 

